text: Gennady Samosedenko (born 25 February 1942) is a Russian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chelyabinsk
